                        была недавно обнаружена в музейных фондах.</seg>
                     <seg xml:lang="en">My autopsy in December 2013 showed that the front had suffered recent damage: right half of the inscription was chipped off.
                     According to D.V. Zhuravlev, this chipped off fragment has since been rediscovered in the museum storage.</seg>
